\section{Changes in version 1.0.3 (2014-10-22)}{
                              
\itemize{
  \item \code{se.PPSfit} and \code{GoF.PPSfit} functions are now S3 methods.
  \item \code{dPPS}, \code{pPPS}, \code{qPPS}, \code{hPPS} and \code{rPPS} functions accept now vector for their parameter arguments. They also accept standard arguments as \code{lower.tail}, \code{log.p} and \code{log}.
  \item Some improvements in code quality. For example, avoiding to grow vectors. The code has been commented.
  \item \code{ADGofTest} and \code{lmom} \R packages are moved from depends to imports.
  \item Some of the function documentation have been combined using alias.
  \item NEWS and CITATION files included.
  \item New \code{forbes400} and \code{turkey} datasets and examples using them included.
  }
}

